# Release Checklist

- [ ] Critical user flows smoke-tested
- [ ] Migrations applied on target environment
- [ ] Types regenerated if schema changed
- [ ] Env vars present (no secrets in client)
- [ ] RLS/policies verified for touched tables
- [ ] Role redirects correct (cashier vs admin)
- [ ] Public routes stay public (menu/QR)
- [ ] No demo/fake KPIs on production pages
- [ ] Error monitoring / logs checked if configured
- [ ] Rollback path known for risky changes
